name: baron lanteigne 2021-06-13 #HENthousand
description: I'm joining the #HENthousand challenge with this one. What you see here is a sneak peak of my upcoming project, Manibus. This first test was captured live from the blender viewport with AI denoising which gives it the style transfer look.
